<li>"All Show, No Go: Land Reform in the Philippines," <i>The Nation</i>, 11 May 1974, pages 586–589.</li>
<li>
<i>Testimony about conditions in the Philippines</i>, U.S. Senate, Subcommittee on Foreign Operations (24 May 1974), and House of Representatives, Subcommittee on Asian and Pacific Affairs (5 June 1974). Printed in the <i>Congressional Record</i>, 120 (4 June 1974): S-9564-70.</li>
<li>"Land Reform in the Philippines Since the Marcos Coup," <i>Pacific Affairs,</i> 47 (Fall 1974): pages 286-304.</li>
